{"word":"ὑπεροράω","slug":"ὑπεροράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπεροράω</b></el> <el>(ionic <el>-έω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-όψομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-εῖδον</el>) (<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>-ῐδεῖν</el>) (aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ὑπερώφθην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to look over, look down upon</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to overlook, slight, despise</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to shew contempt for</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}